title: IBEX-Hi Release-14; Compton-Getting, no Survival-Probability, ram-direction 3-year-Average West Ecliptic Pressure andFlux Power-Law Slope Maps - Dr. David J. McComas (Princeton University)

parameters.description: ---> Above as X/Y image.
